---

const approaches = [
  {
    title: "Compassion",
    description:
      "We meet you where you are, with gentleness and compassion.",
  },
  {
    title: "Dignity",
    description:
      "Your values, beliefs, and autonomy are at the center of everything we do.",
  },
  {
    title: "Respect for Your Story",
    description:
      "We honor your unique journey, your voice, and the meaning you bring to this chapter of life.",
  },
  {
    title: "Spiritual Connection",
    description:
      "For those who seek it, we create space for reflection, ritual, and connection to something greater—whatever that means to you. Honoring the unique beliefs, traditions, and questions that give your life depth and direction.",
  },
];
---

<div class="mt-16 md:mt-0">
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-[#393836]">
        Our Approach
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Introductory Paragraphs -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center text-[#575654] space-y-6 mb-16">
      <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg text-[#575654] leading-relaxed">
        At the heart of our work is a simple but powerful belief: 
        <strong>each person’s story matters—deeply.</strong>
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        We know that serious illness, loss, caregiving, and aging are not just medical or logistical experiences—they are emotional, relational, and often spiritual. That’s why our approach is holistic and person-centered, offering care that honors the full complexity of your experience.
      </p>
      <p class="font-serif text-2xl text-[#332e76] italic">
        We don’t rush. We don’t prescribe.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Instead, we offer a steady, compassionate presence—a place where you can feel safe, supported, and truly heard.
      </p>
    </div>

      <!-- Heart Divider -->
    <div class="relative flex justify-center mb-16">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="w-full border-t border-gray-300/70"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative flex justify-center">
            <span class="bg-[#fbfaf8] px-4">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-[#332e76]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12z" />
                </svg>
            </span>
        </div>
    </div>

  <!-- Approaches -->
  <div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-12">
      {
        approaches.map((item) => (
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#e3efee] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-[#332e76]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">{item.title}</h3>{" "}
              <p class="text-[#575654] leading-relaxed">{item.description}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>


  <!-- Concluding Statement -->
  <div class="mt-5 text-center pt-12">
      <p class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl text-[#393836] max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          "Whether in conversation, silence, or shared grief, we hold space with intention, helping you feel grounded and accompanied."
      </p>
  </div>
        <!-- Heart Divider -->
    <div class="relative flex justify-center mt-10">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="w-full border-t border-gray-300/70"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative flex justify-center">
            <span class="bg-[#fbfaf8] px-4">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-[#332e76]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12z" />
                </svg>
            </span>
        </div>
</div>

</div>